CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1946, pg. 10, reads: "Enjoying Gala Week - Mrs. Irma Robertson, wife of Lieut. James Robertson of the police force, laughs with Mrs. Viola Williams, her good friend, over the fun at Loendi Club. They celebrated with the Frogs this week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Irma Robertson and Viola Williams, seated on sofa with chrome arms, in front of large glass block window, in Loendi Club for FROGS week event
